show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा 
https://kukufm.com/show/the-phoenix-conspiracy/?utm_source=share_sh
show.description: When a hardened private investigator takes on what seems like a routine case, he's drawn into a shadowy world controlled by a secretive organization and its mysterious leader known only as Phoenix. His life spirals into chaos after falling for a woman married to one of the organization's key players. As their forbidden relationship deepens, the two become entangled in a lethal game of deception where loyalty is currency and trust can be fatal. With enemies lurking in every shadow and the line between ally and adversary increasingly blurred, they must navigate a treacherous conspiracy where the price of truth may be their lives.
